# Map site subfolders -> local source folders (one row per mini-app).
# Column separator: TAB (recommended) or first space after the name.
#
# Rules:
# - If the source has package.json: runs npm install && npm run build, copies dist/ into <name>/
# - Else if the source has index.html at its root: copies that folder into <name>/ (static mini-app)
#
# Example rows (use your own paths):
#
# candlescan	/Users/you/projects/candlescan
# myotherapp	/Users/you/projects/myotherapp
